HEADWORD: Pina
<hw>Pi"na</hw> <pr>(<it>pron. also</it> <?/)</pr>.
<fld>(Metal.)</fld> <def>A cone of silver amalgam prepared for
retorting; also, the residuary cone of spongy silver left after the
retorting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

